{"tid":857620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同大家講個笑話，真係好好笑 haha","createTime":"2018-10-11T08:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T05:22:36.000Z","uid":69221,"like":85,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"989800c3931c6ed5ef9e5625f6482c2e49f75725","tid":857620,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n是咁的，haha<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n森林住左班小動物，有一年大灰狼黎左講笑話，佢話:我講完你地是旦一隻唔笑嘅，我就捉一隻做祭品！<br />\n狼開始講：「鄧小平應該拎和平獎」，所有動物都笑到肚痛，惟獨成班豬唔笑，於是河童就被捉走左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二年，狼又黎講笑話「我地唔洗去中國，香港已經係中國」講完之後，所有動物都笑到肚痛，惟獨班豬又唔笑，於是鹿仔就被捉走左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第三年狼冇黎，不過黎左月鵝<br />\n佢話「維尼真係好有魅力」<br />\n所有動物都不笑，惟獨班豬笑到肚痛。<br />\n大家忍不住要問豬，點解會覺得佢個笑話好笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿豬邊笑邊答：「哈哈！因為，我終於諗到，隻狼個笑話點解咁好笑喇，哈哈哈！」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebcb57afcec762e05395c499a3dab71dba8d5ff","tid":857620,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:17:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ea7268e5b95b7b2bcca8c6bd4b8710ec112b625","tid":857620,"uid":174345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:17:52.000Z","msg":"有含意"},{"pid":"78f067becc3b35511f87a55881d08b3b8987fb6a","tid":857620,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"蝦蝦"},{"pid":"223497bf3e09a08623f6bbdfc67e271faacf2a77","tid":857620,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78f067becc3b35511f87a55881d08b3b8987fb6a","tid":857620,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"蝦蝦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:23:20.000Z","msg":"Haha蝦腸"},{"pid":"fe6aa510f7af98dbb3121c5f6e4aa557655bc33b","tid":85762